text: Haha, are you sure about that?

It's the same thing as me wearing a mask...
So you can't possible know who I am!

Haha, what's with you!
You're just covering your eyes with your own hands!

True, I don't have a fancy mask like yours, Yuika...
It's a DIY mask.

Why bother when you're not trying to get away with it~?
Covering your eyes like that is practically a red flag!

If you want to joke around, you'll have to use a bit
more brain power, okay? Like Mitsumine.
